---
import ConditionPage from '../../components/ConditionPage.astro';
---
<ConditionPage
	title="Treatment in Clapham"
	highlight="Multiple Sclerosis"
	heroSubtitle="MS affects everyone differently, which means your treatment needs to be tailored to you. We help you stay active, independent and in control."
	breadcrumb="Multiple Sclerosis"
	seoTitle="Multiple Sclerosis Treatment in Clapham"
	seoDescription="Specialist MS physiotherapy in Clapham, London. Tailored neurological rehab to improve mobility, balance, strength and manage fatigue day to day."
	introImage="/condition/multiple-sclerosis/woman-hiking.jpg"
	whoImage="/condition/multiple-sclerosis/woman-laughing.jpg"
	intro={[
		"Multiple Sclerosis (MS) affects everyone differently, which means your treatment needs to be tailored to you. We focus on helping you stay active, maintain independence, and manage your symptoms in a practical way.",
		"Whether you've just been diagnosed or have been living with MS for years, we'll build a plan around your goals, your energy levels and the things that matter most to you.",
	]}
	symptomsHeading="When to get"
	symptomsHighlight="support"
	symptomsIntro="Physiotherapy can help if you're experiencing any of the following:"
	symptomsList={[
		"Difficulty walking or changes in your gait",
		"Problems with balance or coordination",
		"Muscle stiffness or spasms",
		"Ongoing fatigue that affects daily activities",
		"Muscle weakness or reduced strength",
		"Numbness or altered sensation",
		"Pain",
	]}
	treatmentHeading="How we"
	treatmentHighlight="help"
	treatmentIntro="Your plan is shaped around your symptoms and goals, and may include:"
	treatmentList={[
		"Physiotherapy to improve strength, mobility, and coordination",
		"Exercises tailored to your energy levels and goals",
		"Balance and gait training",
		"Advice on pacing and managing fatigue",
		"Pain relief and current pain pathway support",
		"Hydrotherapy where appropriate",
	]}
	whoHeading="Who we"
	whoHighlight="help"
	whoList={[
		"Recently diagnosed patients",
		"People recovering after a relapse",
		"Those managing long-term symptoms",
		"Individuals with poorly controlled pain",
		"Those seeking to maintain fitness",
		"People experiencing mobility or balance changes",
	]}
	faqs={[
		{ q: "Can physiotherapy help with MS fatigue?", a: "Yes. the right type of exercise can actually help improve energy levels. We\\'ll guide you on pacing and recovery." },
		{ q: "Is it safe to exercise with MS?", a: "Yes. Exercise is important for maintaining strength and mobility, and we tailor everything to your ability." },
		{ q: "What is hydrotherapy?", a: "Exercise in warm water can make movement easier and more comfortable, especially if you have weakness or stiffness." },
		{ q: "Do I need a referral?", a: "No. you can book directly with us." },
	]}
/>
